  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>As a tech, you may be required to add services and/or parts to a ticket as you make repairs. To do this you need to edit the ticket you are working on.</p><p /><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Look up the ticket by the ticket number or the device serial number. See\u00a0<a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933541674/Searching+for+Tickets\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933541674\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Searching for Tickets</a> </p></li><li><p>Click the edit button to edit the ticket</p></li><li><p>OPTIONAL: Click on the &quot;Ticket Items&quot; tab to focus on the ticket items section.</p></li><li><p>Add ticket item(s) for the parts &amp; services you need to add to the ticket</p><ul><li><p>Look up the item to add or search for an item in the &quot;Add Item&quot; search box.</p></li><li><p>Click the &quot;Add Item&quot; button when you have selected the item you want</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Quick Add: Scan or type the SKU or Serial Number of the item you want to add and press enter</p></li></ul></li><li><p>When you are done adding ticket items, click the &quot;Save&quot; button at the bottom</p></li></ol><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933476043/Add%20Parts%20and%20Service%201.png?api=v2\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1933476043/Add%20Parts%20and%20Service%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p />",
